x7嘅邏輯邊度錯啦傻仔"},{"pid":"8c0a17197eea1bb971277f909d4a24b6990ecc27","tid":927823,"uid":17232,"like":18,"dislike":7,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"淨係睇上面幾個人嘅留言就知香港太多傻閪<br />\n數學定義上嘅multiplication就係commutative<br />\n從來就無規定過乘法裡面嘅乘數同被乘數一定要代表啲乜，上面幾個連數學都未撚學好就急住做老師話啲小朋友邏輯錯。好心自己進修吓數學先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd14eb7f3b82fbeb6e53675cc58c095473dbb3b","tid":927823,"uid":106341,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T17:22:58.000Z","msg":"話要分次序嗰d一定係文科仔"},{"pid":"d86b3bc55151e0af9c65f9e5233da1b581b7715e","tid":927823,"uid":152585,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2cd14eb7f3b82fbeb6e53675cc58c095473dbb3b","tid":927823,"uid":106341,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T17:22:58.000Z","msg":"話要分次序嗰d一定係文科仔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:51:47.000Z","msg":"工人每天整85米 = 85 x 7<br />\n<br />\n整咗6個星期 = 85 x 7 x 6<br />\n<br />\n係數學上 同一條式入面7同6倒轉緊係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n但85 x 6 係咩意思？<br />\n<br />\n旁邊直式係要分2次計<br />\n<br />\n85米同6星期如果冇&lsquo;每天&rsquo;係中間係解唔通"},{"pid":"49126ad7d7b752703e71165ad38f7287240cf629","tid":927823,"uid":56240,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d86b3bc55151e0af9c65f9e5233da1b581b7715e","tid":927823,"uid":152585,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2cd14eb7f3b82fbeb6e53675cc58c095473dbb3b","tid":927823,"uid":106341,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T17:22:58.000Z","msg":"話要分次序嗰d一定係文科仔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:51:47.000Z","msg":"工人每天整85米 = 85 x 7<br />\n<br />\n整咗6個星期 = 85 x 7 x 6<br />\n<br />\n係數學上 同一條式入面7同6倒轉緊係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n但85 x 6 係咩意思？<br />\n<br />\n旁邊直式係要分2次計<br />\n<br />\n85米同6星期如果冇&lsquo;每天&rsquo;係中間係解唔通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"85 m/day * 6 weeks * 7days/week<br />\n自己cancel d  symbol 啦<br />\n最尾咪又係得番個m<br />\n咁都話解唔通???<img src=\"/assets